Title: Open Source Friday: Archestra – Secure platform for enterprise agents with MCP
Description:
Join us this Open Source Friday to explore Archestra, an innovative open-source platform designed for secure, scalable enterprise agents, powered by MCP. Deploy, manage, and orchestrate AI and software securely with advanced model governance and access controls

Get hands-on with demos, contribute to the codebase, and connect with the Archestra community. Let’s build the future of enterprise automation together—securely and openly!
